-- Rouble falls to record-low vs dollar of 38.00 roubles
-- By Alexander Wining and Lidia Kelly
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 02:13AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Sept 15 (Reuters) - The Russian rouble hit fresh historic lows against the dollar on Monday, falling to 38 roubles per dollar, with investors concerned about Moscow's response to the new wave of Western sanctions.

